Electron Cash - Simple Ledger Protocol Edition

Version 1 Features
-----
- Simple Ledger Protocol (SLP) token transaction capability
- Local DAG validation engine (limited to depth of X)
- Proxy DAG validation (using bitdb)
- Have disable option for SLP (facilitates merging code into EC master repo)


Planned Version 2 Features
-----
- Add UI/UX for INIT/MINT batons
- Add UI/UX for issuer COMM tranasactions
- Restructure wallet file to include token names dict
- Bolster token saftey, make sure token loss is 100% prevented in edge cases when not in txo
